{"tid":1984613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一張圖話你知黃營唔可以繼續小圈子落去","createTime":"2020-04-22T14:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T01:41:41.000Z","uid":225100,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"778ccf68ef175d193ef5ffdd4739bc66e9178cff","tid":1984613,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:34:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQUiuCb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQUiuCb.png&h=1dce76a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//THEpaperskin :<br />\n個骨牌圖 <span style=\"color: red;\">紅色係一條直線</span>，比如中央嘅命令係直接下達，而中共港共嘅行為會直接激起黃色嘅人嘅反應。但黃色要先經過一個塔（上咗神枱嘅人？大台？）再去一個小圈子，同現實嘅情況一樣，先經過一啲上咗神枱嘅人/大台嘅發言，再擴散去<span style=\"color: gold;\">小圈子</span>嘅思考。黃色嘅反應會激起藍色，但<span style=\"color: blue;\">藍色嘅人係一個大圈子，比起黃色佢哋團結好多</span>，亦冇經過咁多複雜嘅過程，所以反應快速而直接，動員能力強。最後先去到綠色，亦都係人數最多，反應時間最長嘅中立派。<br />\n<br />\n唔夠膽講睇得出咩寓意，但<span style=\"color: gold;\">我哋要學識主動接收第一手資訊</span>，而唔係靠嗰啲IG Fb kol出post先了解當下時局，因為嗰啲人往往都已經有自己立場，就好似演算法咁，佢哋俾得你睇嘅嘢一定係佢哋關注嘅嘢，並唔全面。又，好多人其實講嘢都係好似孫文咁好空泛，剩係得一個概念，雖然唔可以話係假希望，但聽咗好似冇聽咁（好似我呢個留言咁）。不過現實時局的確唔係咁簡單直接，已經唔係再停留於街頭抗爭嘅時間，香港人對國際政治認識太少，先導致佢哋<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">盲目</span></strong>相信唔同人（沈大師之類）講嘅嘢，現實情況係，唔會有一條片或者一個人可以教識你點樣贏，所以，<span style=\"color: gold;\">睇多啲新聞啦</span>。//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>個人睇法</em>: <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">黃營太過小圈子 好難影響倒更多中立嘅人 </span><br />\n(圖入面冇一條路去影響綠色區域)<br />\n最後益咗藍營<br />\n<br />\n而中立其實都唔止一隻色<br />\n唔同嘅綠色關注嘅野都唔同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">讀多啲書 睇多啲新聞<br />\n聽多啲唔同perspective嘅意見<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔好聽死一兩個KOL大台</span><br />\n咁先至會知道用咩方法說服中間派 改變中間派 <br />\n令更多人加入我哋</span></span><br />\n<br />\ntldr<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黃營唔可以繼續小圈子落去<br />\n要裝備自己 用行動影響中間派!!!!</span></span>"},{"pid":"eef08e04aee21ca7faca3980191e718167f394d9","tid":1984613,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"獨派手足更加係<br />\n如果獨派係黃骨牌<br />\n咁綠骨牌就係淺黃<br />\n獨派要做多啲去宣傳獨立 宣揚本土意識<br />\n唔係就會益咗。。。。"},{"pid":"63efd2af3dc9d448143eaf1d53cfc2cc2fe91f6f","tid":1984613,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11fb62ed167200550fd8f6443b4d2b9a3379f154","tid":1984613,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:40:02.000Z","msg":"source: 《孫文的野望》第五集 1:46<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vvzfuAUPvPs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvvzfuAUPvPs&d=uNNx3RetO4MSseDCYlD6CtjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=c980e5a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vvzfuAUPvPs</a>"},{"pid":"2910910b157ab28f397cbe41b8e1f9dac2c5a192","tid":1984613,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:40:34.000Z","msg":"香港人生性唔認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各區要人- dse散場派選民登記表(已簡約整合)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1984588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1984588</a>"},{"pid":"a442377aed7507b91df9f0a6ae4d24bacac14d5a","tid":1984613,"uid":205721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"17dc2f1e20e2fb992abbb6e8449979beafeabd20","tid":1984613,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a442377aed7507b91df9f0a6ae4d24bacac14d5a","tid":1984613,"uid":205721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd882c6b08286a712523af98f4b162d7f305b0e","tid":19846